'''Beta-4 CardSharks''' were a type [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] [[Dealer droid/Legends|dealer droid]]. They walked unsteadily and could also help clean up areas. This appears to be the extent of their programming. The [[Neimoidian/Legends|Neimoidian]] [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]]-owner, [[Groshik]], had such a [[Droid/Legends|droid]] in his [[Cantina/Legends|cantina]] on [[Apatros/Legends|Apatros]]. The droid was owned by the [[Outer Rim Oreworks Company]].<ref name="PoD">''[[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction]]''</ref>

